  "title": "⚙️TECHNICAL SERVICES TECHNICIAN @ WEST | UP TO $2.5K + ALLOWANCE, TRANSPORT & MEALS",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>⚙️TECHNICAL SERVICES TECHNICIAN @ WEST | UP TO $2.5K + ALLOWANCE, TRANSPORT & MEALS</strong></u></p><p>📍Location: Jurong East </p><p>💰Salary: $2,000-$2,500 + Night shift allowance + Allowance for meals and transport  </p><p>🗓️Working days: Alternate 4/3 days a week  </p><p>🕑Shift hours:   </p><p>7.45pm-7.55am  </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Operate manufacturing equipment to meet production schedules, output targets, and quality standards. </p></li><li><p>Provide technical support and troubleshooting to minimize downtime and maintain production efficiency. </p></li><li><p>Carry out daily and monthly preventive maintenance to ensure equipment reliability and optimal performance. </p></li><li><p>Actively participate in workplace safety practices and continuous quality improvement initiatives. </p></li></ul><p>Requirements:  </p><ul><li><p>NITEC in Engineering/related discipline </p></li><li><p>Able to work 12h shifts and overtime if necessary </p></li><li><p>Physically fit to carry 15kg loads </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
